r1 tping 100 120 2.2.2.2 vrf v1 sou lo0
r1 tping 100 120 4321::2 vrf v1 sou lo0
r1 tping 100 120 9.9.2.2 vrf v2
!r1 tping 100 120 9992::2 vrf v2
r1 tping 100 120 9.9.3.2 vrf v3
!r1 tping 100 120 9993::2 vrf v3
